    "It can be attested that the nature of thinking about major unsolved issues for decades demotivated some students.",
    "Afterwards, the repetitive cycle was expressed as one of the weaknesses of PBL by 3 (12%) participants.",
    "Having considered the figures, it can be stated that breaking the monotony can be effective in reversing this vicious cycle.",
    "The final weakness of PBL was pointed out as chaotic by one (4%) participant.",
    "Having taken it into consideration, it is safe to claim that discussing the themes under the leadership of the teacher was a tough task during controversial sessions."
